Class HeaderFieldList

java.lang.Object
  org.jpws.pwslib.data.RawFieldList
      org.jpws.pwslib.data.HeaderFieldList
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable
public class HeaderFieldList
extends RawFieldList

A descendant of RawFieldList that limits the range of valid elements to field types 0..254 and supplies additional functionality specific to headerfield lists.

Since:
2-0-0
